Description:
Wayeal is a publicly listed scientific & industrial instruments manufacturer, founded in 2003, total staff 1400+, among which 30% are engineers & 25 nos of PhDs.
We have 4 product lines,
1. Analytical instruments: HPLC, UHPLC, IC, GC, AAS, LC-MS,GC-MS, consumables, etc.;
2. Industrial leak detector & system: Helium MS Leak Detector, Vacuum Chamber HLD System, Pressure Decay Leak Tester & System;
3. Environment monitoring systems: AQMS, WQMS, CEMS, LGA, VOCs;
4. Medical device: qPCR, dPCR, Ultrasonic Scalpel.

Wayeal has served hundreds of leading universities, institutes, World TOP 500 companies in 20+ countries. We're aiming to build a world famous brand & long-run win-win ecosystem of partners worldwide.

We have 4 product lines,
1. Laboratory analytical instruments, incl. HPLC, UHPLC, IC, GC, AAS, UV-vis, LC-MS, consumables, etc.;
2. Industrial leak detector & system, incl. Helium MS Leak Detector, Vacuum Chamber HLD System, Pressure Decay Leak Tester & System;
3. Environment online monitoring systems, incl. AQMS, WQMS, CEMS, LGA;
4. Medical device, incl. qPCR, dPCR, Ultrasonic Scalpel, Hemodialyzer.

Wayeal has served hundreds of leading universities, institutes, World TOP 500 companies & MNC branches in 20+ countries. We're aiming to build a world famous brand &long-run win-win ecosystem of partners worldwide.

Energy monitoring circuit by circuit to work out where your business is using energy, perhaps unnecessarily;

Multi-utility monitoring including gas and water usage;

Retrofit automation in breweries, food processors, wind farms.

In-line acoustic emission (AE)-based condition monitoring of heavily loaded, low-speed (roller) bearings. 
- (offhore) heavy lifting;
- (offshore) wind;
- FPSOs and turrets;
- Infrastructure.

By capturing and analyzing high-frequency acoustic signatures, the specific degradation mechanisms can be identified, their progression characterized, and the damage location within the bearing precisely determined. 

If this information is systematically incorporated into maintenance decisions, the result is maintenance that is predictable, substantiated, and responsible. 

A sector in which clarity is the norm and reliability is the result.
